AS3 UTILS
http://github.com/percentjuice/as3utils
common actionscript chores... made simple.

INSTALLATION
This is an AS3 library, a compiled swc is included.    

LIBRARIES REQUIRED FOR BUILD
AS3-Signals -- https://github.com/robertpenner/as3-signals

LIBRARIES REQUIRED TO RUN TESTS
Hamcrest-AS3 -- https://github.com/drewbourne/hamcrest-as3
AS3-Signals Utilities-Async -- https://github.com/eidiot/as3-signals-utilities-async
Mockito_Flex -- https://bitbucket.org/loomis/mockito-flex/wiki/Home
flex Unit -- http://flexunit.org/